          <h2 class='text-2xl font-medium tracking-tight text-slate-700 md:text-3xl'>为什么选我们</h2>
        </div>

        <div class='mt-10 grid w-full gap-6 md:grid-cols-3'>
          <div class='pt-2 text-center'>
            <div class='text-xs tracking-[0.2em] text-slate-400 uppercase'>服务案例</div>
            <div class='mt-3 text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900' data-count-up='3000'>0+</div>
            <div class='mt-2 text-sm text-slate-500'>暖通 · 空气 · 看板</div>
